abstract: "LOOK. No seams!" a student boasted, holding aloft a dress she had recently completed.  Making a garment without visible seams is one of the proudest achievements of many students learning dress designing and clothing construction at the French Fashion Academy, 600 Madison Avenue (near 57th Street).
